title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Sim Update V - Orbis Flying Eye Hospital
description:
Today Asobo released Sim Update V. As part of this Sim Update also a new aircraft became available. The Orbis Flying Eye Hospital which is a MacDonell Douglas MD10. If you are getting really exited I must disappoint you. Although the aircraft has been added it cannot fly. If this will happen someone in the future that is still a secret I think ;-)

In this video I will show you how you can get the aircraft so you can have a look how the flying eye hospital looks from the inside.
